; Regression test for issue #2980:
; Register average report broken with distributed expenses.
;
; When --collapse is active with --monthly --average, collapse_posts may
; change the displayed account across periods (e.g. from a real account
; to <Total> and back).  The per-account running total seeding from
; PR #2909 would fail to find the new account in its accumulator map,
; resetting the running total to zero and producing incorrect averages.
;
; Fixed by disabling per-account period averaging when --collapse or
; --depth is in the handler chain, since collapse already reduces
; multi-account periods to single posts.

2025/12/31 * Annual Distributed Expense
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/01/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/02/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/03/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/04/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/05/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/06/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/07/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/08/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/09/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/10/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                          $1,000    ; [2025/11/01]
    Expenses:Subscriptions                            $500    ; [2025/12/01]
    Assets:Checking

2025/12/01 * Monthly Expense
    Expenses:Entertainment                      $500
    Assets:Checking

2026/01/01 * Monthly Expense
    Expenses:Entertainment                      $1,000
    Assets:Checking

2026/02/01 * Monthly Expense
    Expenses:Entertainment                      $1,000
    Assets:Checking

test --monthly --average --collapse reg Expenses
25-Jan-01 - 25-Jan-31           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Feb-01 - 25-Feb-28           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Mar-01 - 25-Mar-31           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Apr-01 - 25-Apr-30           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-May-01 - 25-May-31           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Jun-01 - 25-Jun-30           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Jul-01 - 25-Jul-31           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Aug-01 - 25-Aug-31           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Sep-01 - 25-Sep-30           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Oct-01 - 25-Oct-31           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Nov-01 - 25-Nov-30           Expenses:Subscriptions       $1,000       $1,000
25-Dec-01 - 25-Dec-31           <Total>                      $1,000       $1,000
26-Jan-01 - 26-Jan-31           Expenses:Entertainment       $1,000       $1,000
26-Feb-01 - 26-Feb-28           Expenses:Entertainment       $1,000       $1,000
end test
